Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:53.46,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs72\an7\c&HA842B4&\3c&H692C6E&\bord9\pos(90,29.999)}浑沌\N\N{\fs36\3c&HD2E8F0&\c&H1F3139&\bord11.999}诺福克㹴。众所周知是里练马的老大。格外钟爱颓废与混沌，穷凶极恶。\N吹嘘日本狼的灭绝是因为自己全吃了。\N相比于用暴力统治，更擅长找出人的弱点再纠缠不休。\N擅长揭露心理创伤，在贬低对方，给予屈辱时会感到无上的幸福。\N总之，是个超会给人添乱的小狗。
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.95,0:03:55.39,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不止是浑沌 他部下的件、橄榄球员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:54.71,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs72\an7\c&HA842B4&\3c&H692C6E&\bord9\pos(90,29.999)}件\N\N{\fs36\3c&HD2E8F0&\c&H1F3139&\bord11.999}半人半牛的妖怪。会四面八方喷洒母乳，一旦喷射自己无法停止。\N母乳是酸性的，碰到身体会引起强烈的瘙痒，继而生出莫名其妙的疹子。\N四个全季节轮胎取代了腿，使之可以在任何地方疾行。当然燃料也是母乳。\N非常恐惧断奶。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:55.21,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs72\an7\c&HA842B4&\3c&H692C6E&\bord9\pos(790,40.5)}橄榄球员\N{\fs24.001}\h\N{\fs36\3c&HD2E8F0&\c&H1F3139&\bord11.999}想成为棒球选手的英式橄榄球选手。所以经常会说「来击球吧」\N「好球」之类的棒球用语。对英式橄榄球没有爱，\N所以被人同美式橄榄球混淆也无所谓。\N乘坐的快艇动力是水，拍拍就会变快。\N偶尔也会心情不好，无视橄榄球员的意志暴走去随心所欲的地方\N（主要是千川大街和旧早稻田大街）。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:55.96,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs72\an7\c&HA842B4&\3c&H692C6E&\bord9\pos(90,29.999)}三毛猫\N\N{\fs36\3c&HD2E8F0&\c&H1F3139&\bord11.999}稀有的雄性三花猫。将爱丽丝引入里练马的罪魁祸首。自称游戏狂。\N从不懈怠锻炼但那肌肉锻炼法不会有反效果吗？\N问道为何锻炼肌肉时，他直言道：\N「为了抢走新发售的硬件软件再逃跑」\N讨厌射击游戏、动作游戏、RPG和模拟游戏。
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.39,0:03:57.84,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,三毛猫、序二段、罪恶感化身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:56.46,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs72\an7\c&HA842B4&\3c&H692C6E&\bord9\pos(696,29.999)}序二段\N\N{\fs36\3c&HD2E8F0&\c&H1F3139&\bord11.999}被作为活人牺牲品的序二段力士的转生。\N身上的设计是那时的残余，但也有传言说那是自己画的。\N想了解详细信息请搜索柳条人。\N很后悔只在相扑上达到序二段，\N但似乎查不到这位力士的信息，\N所以也可能只是一个胖子在欺诈。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.84,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs72\an7\c&HA842B4&\3c&H692C6E&\bord9\pos(90,29.999)}罪恶感化身\N\N{\fs36\3c&HD2E8F0&\c&H1F3139&\bord11.999}人如其名，是聚集了世间一切罪恶感，具象化的产物。\N仅凭此可能会给人难缠的想象，但实际性格清爽。\N显然遇事先道歉解决了不少事，触怒别人时也是。\N有时会从头上射出罪恶光线来攻击。罪恶光线舔起来是酸的。\N大概是黑醋的味道。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:04:00.38,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs72\an7\c&HA842B4&\3c&H692C6E&\bord9\pos(55.499,416.999)}暮蝉、油蝉以及其余四分之一\N\N{\fs36\3c&HD2E8F0&\c&H1F3139&\bord11.999}本人称是集合了蝉优点的精英，实际上只是杂种。是少见的不会装死的蝉，装死立刻就会暴露。\N受到了「全日本蝉装死协会」的持续严重关注。此外还经常被别的蝉装死骗到。\N因为反应很有趣所以得到了周围的大好评。
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.84,0:04:00.63,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,暮蝉、油蝉以及其余四分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:02.17,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs72\an7\c&HA842B4&\3c&H692C6E&\bord9\pos(90,29.999)}步兵\N\N{\fs36\3c&HD2E8F0&\c&H1F3139&\bord11.999}将棋的步。口音很重，且没有法则。明明很弱却都在逞威风。\N好汉不吃眼前亏，过着无忧无虑的生活。
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.63,0:04:03.28,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,还有敌方的杂兵步兵对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:04.93,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我果然还是害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.38,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,没事的抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:10.72,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,说是练爱乐园是按最终回的状态复现的
Comment: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:14.52,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs29.999\an7\c&HD2E8FA&\3c&HD2E8FA&\bord9\pos(259.501,36)}Episode 25\N\NA Doggone Loser Yowls!\NBut Only the Norfolk Terrier
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.27,0:04:14.52,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs29.999\an7\c&HC5CD52&\3c&HAF7F81&\bord2.999\pos(257.862,99.819)}\N\N丧家犬狺狺狂吠 只是个诺福克㹴罢了
Comment: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:14.52,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs36\bord9\c&HD2E8FA&\3c&HD2E8FA&\pos(1455,36)}Top 3 Important Items in NeriAli
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.27,0:04:14.52,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs36\bord2.999\c&HC5CD52&\3c&HAF7F81&\pos(1471.381,90)}练爱三大重要物品是这些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:14.52,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs24.001\bord6.001\c&H192D37&\3c&HC1DAE6&\frz15.63\pos(1114.501,177.001)}①持驹之泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:14.52,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs24.001\bord6.001\c&H192D37&\3c&HC1DAE6&\frz11.7\pos(1120.499,607.5)}②俄罗斯智能马桶盖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:14.52,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs24.001\bord6.001\c&H192D37&\3c&HC1DAE6&\frz359.7\pos(1411.501,577.501)}③枭首之镰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:11.68,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:16.36,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,他们打败了浑沌一伙 并封印进了将棋驹袋里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.27,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:20.16,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,变成步兵的人真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:21.55,Default,Alice,0,0,0,,小苏 你好慢！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:23.32,Default,Alice,0,0,0,,把脖子上的绳子摘下来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.03,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.95,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,摘下来我就得死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:27.58,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,{\an8}这是我的本体！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:29.41,Default,Opie,0,0,0,,被件他们捉到了就要死刑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:31.00,Default,Opie,0,0,0,,怎样都会死啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:33.12,Default,Alice,0,0,0,,拷问铁！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:34.52,Default,Iron Monty,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:37.73,Default,Iron Monty,0,0,0,,问！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:40.67,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,要死要死要死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:42.38,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,拷问铁是S吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.59,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,他是个职业的拷问士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:46.94,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,对拷问很自豪来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:50.18,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,但是他自己最讨厌疼痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:53.24,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那个一直自杀未遂的就是小苏？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:53.91,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:57.04,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,然后那个受伤了就会喷出不妙的液体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:59.58,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,让大家都很嗨的就是罂粟粟？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:03.59,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,因为是基因重组的 所以对人体无害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:04.78,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 有人追上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:05.59,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,老大？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:06.58,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,他是浑沌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:08.54,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,因为他像馄饨所以叫馄饨？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:11.86,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,有这部分原因 但我觉得不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.86,0:05:13.74,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,字要复杂一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:14.72,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:19.12,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,我昨天想到了很好的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:22.21,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,感觉爱丽丝他们根本没可能赢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.37,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:26.27,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,里大泉世界虽然很混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.27,0:05:28.28,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,但其实全在将棋棋盘上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:31.43,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,不管什么行为 都要遵守将棋的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:34.36,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,就这样 察觉到这点的爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:37.24,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,使用夹将棋的规则击败了浑沌他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:37.24,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,夹将棋：通过己方棋子夹击来吃掉对方棋子\N只是用了将棋棋盘和部分棋子（步兵、成步）\N与将棋规则关系不大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:39.16,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,成功回到了练爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:42.30,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,但是 之后还有很厉害的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:43.13,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,啊 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:45.33,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我说到兴头剧透了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:46.87,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:47.84,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,完全没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:48.78,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.86,0:05:57.53,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,燃起来了的感觉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:08.15,Default,Stall Walker 1,0,0,0,,欢迎欢迎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:09.05,Default,Stall Walker 1,0,0,0,,恶劣欢迎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:10.28,Default,Stall Walker 2,0,0,0,,便宜便宜！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:11.23,Default,Stall Walker 2,0,0,0,,便宜到炸！
Comment: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:13.22,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnTimes New Roman\bord9\c&H98B3D8&\3c&H98B3D8&\pos(880.499,171)}Signature Gutton Candy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.22,0:06:13.22,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnTimes New Roman\bord2.999\c&H92186B&\3c&HA578B8&\pos(880.499,171)}{\c&H4DDCE8&\3c&H494272&}肠花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:13.23,Default,Stall Walker 3,0,0,0,,死一死看一看！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:15.31,Default,Stall Walker 4,0,0,0,,一串只要三百日元！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.85,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真是的 怎么全是步兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:20.01,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,一个里泉民都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:21.51,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的耶 为啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:22.61,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这啥啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:24.59,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这样的完全不是练爱啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:25.18,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:26.71,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那个 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:28.29,Default,Walker 1,0,0,0,,怎么了 人类女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:30.56,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,今天是什么节日吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:34.12,Default,Walker 1,0,0,0,,我们肯定是在庆祝浑沌大人的胜利日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.85,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？为什么是浑沌？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:36.62,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,爱丽丝呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:38.83,Default,Walker 1,0,0,0,,爱丽丝那群混蛋在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.33,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs54\fscx90\bord9\fnTimes New Roman\c&H4E3737&\3c&HD1C0BE&\frz352.8\fax0.1\pos(535.499,388.501)}爱丽丝之墓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.33,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs47.999\fscx90\bord9\fnTimes New Roman\c&H4E3737&\3c&HD1C0BE&\fax0.15\frz351\pos(1053,469.501)}拷问铁之墓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.33,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs42.001\fscx80\bord9\fnTimes New Roman\c&H4E3737&\3c&HD1C0BE&\fax0.15\frz351\pos(1522.501,537.001)}罂粟粟之墓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.66,0:06:42.52,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,爱丽丝！拷问铁！罂粟粟！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:43.55,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:44.31,Default,Walker 1,0,0,0,,死掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:45.44,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈？开什么玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:46.67,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,只有小苏不在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:49.83,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是为了庆祝爱丽丝他们死掉的节日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:51.78,Default,Walker 1,0,0,0,,无知真可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:54.12,Default,Walker 1,0,0,0,,想用夹将棋战斗的爱丽丽丽丝
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.12,0:06:56.64,Default,Walker 1,0,0,0,,反过来被军人将棋诛灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:56.10,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,军人将棋：相比于将棋更像是军棋\N和将棋没什么关系\N棋子有：大将、中将、少将、\N大佐、中佐、少佐、\N大尉、中尉、少尉、\N飞机、坦克、骑兵、\N工兵、间谍、地雷等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.64,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1148,1)\fs90\bord11.999\fscx90\fnTimes New Roman\c&H4E3737&\3c&HD1C0BE&\pos(949.501,753.001)}爱丽丝之墓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:58.37,Default,Walker 1,0,0,0,,今天就是这样的庆典
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:06:58.97,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你说谎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:00.22,Default,Walker 1,0,0,0,,证据就是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.22,0:07:02.97,Default,Walker 1,0,0,0,,看那边！反抗我们的里泉民的末路！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:04.36,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？哪儿呢？他们在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:08.59,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不可能不可能不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:10.85,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,练爱的世界怎么可能会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:12.31,Default,Walker 1,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:14.69,Default,Walker 1,0,0,0,,来告诉她们吧 四人众
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:17.90,Default,Jonidan,0,0,0,,序二段 由银将转职为工兵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:21.59,Default,Jonidan,0,0,0,,在下设陷阱抓住了那个拷问痴并把他拷问死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:24.83,Default,Quarter,0,0,0,,由桂马转职为骑兵 我们蝉四分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:27.84,Default,Quarter,0,0,0,,把那个药物中毒的踢死了吱吱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:31.25,Default,Guilt Incarnate,0,0,0,,由香车转职为间谍 我 罪恶感化身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.25,0:07:33.29,Default,Guilt Incarnate,0,0,0,,对上吊绳女发动了暗杀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.29,0:07:35.26,Default,Guilt Incarnate,0,0,0,,但是就在那个时候她逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:35.97,Default,Guilt Incarnate,0,0,0,,非常抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:38.10,Default,Calico Cat,0,0,0,,由金将转职为地雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:41.01,Default,Calico Cat,0,0,0,,小生用爆炸杀死了爱丽丝！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:56.58,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\b0\bord6.001\fs54\an9\fnImpact\frz6.144\fax-0.1\pos(1224,18)}{\c&H79477A&\3c&HAAFFF3&}混{\c&H964E8A&}沌{\c&HC0769E&}之{\c&H976F8A&}国{\c&H8A5027&}的\N{\b0\bord6.001\fs54\an9\fnImpact\c&HFCB9D1&\frz6.144\fax-0.1\3c&H8A5027&\pos(1224,18)}浑沌{\c&HB5FAFB&}大人\h
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:42.63,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这样的根本不是练爱！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:43.78,Default,Calico Cat,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:45.82,Default,Calico Cat,0,0,0,,这里是混沌之国的浑沌大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:48.79,Default,Calico Cat,0,0,0,,有进无还的梦幻之国
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:50.56,Default,Calico Cat,0,0,0,,好 很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:50.95,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:52.71,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你擅自说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.71,0:07:53.42,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.42,0:07:55.31,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,随便这是练爱还是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:57.14,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,大家早点去池袋吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:58.91,Default,Quarter,0,0,0,,死刑吱吱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.38,Default,Guilt Incarnate,0,0,0,,抱歉 死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:01.32,Default,Jonidan,0,0,0,,给她们死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.32,0:08:01.87,Default,Calico Cat,0,0,0,,死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:08.27,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,哦？你们哪儿来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:09.84,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,浑身人臭的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:10.60,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:12.18,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,说要去哪儿啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:13.55,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,所以说 去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.47,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,那可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:19.07,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,有个麻烦的家伙让我别让人靠近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.07,0:08:20.42,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,大家 抓住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:22.43,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,别再失败了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:24.39,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,和那群动物的时候一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:25.37,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:26.36,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:27.94,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,总之 现在只能逃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:37.11,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,对了 自动扶梯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:38.28,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:40.41,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你看 真正的练爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:43.08,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,在这里有个进里练马的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:43.91,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:47.41,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,说不定能找个逃跑的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.58,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,哦 果然！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:52.95,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,完全一样！有点感动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:53.82,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,还有还有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:57.35,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那边就是不可思议的世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:58.05,Default,Darkizumiite 1,0,0,0,,饶了我们！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.01,Default,Darkizumiite 2,0,0,0,,什么都没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:00.29,Default,Darkizumiite 3,0,0,0,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:01.32,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这里是哪？
