Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.32,0:09:02.94,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你们干什么呢？
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.94,0:09:05.39,Default,Darkizumiite 3,0,0,0,,我们只是躲在这 别赶我们出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:07.47,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,哼 秘密的藏身地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:09.22,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,抵抗组织！好酷！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:10.29,Default,Darkizumiite 1,0,0,0,,不敢的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:12.41,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,喂 你们在这干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:16.21,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,里泉民不是和爱丽丝幸福的生活在一起吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:20.83,Default,Darkizumiite 3,0,0,0,,本来是这样 但是封印敌人的将棋驹袋突然开了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:22.09,Default,Darkizumiite 3,0,0,0,,浑沌他们逃了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:24.54,Default,Darkizumiite 5,0,0,0,,然后理所当然成了浑沌的天下 变成了现在这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:25.93,Default,Darkizumiite 5,0,0,0,,这样已经一周了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:28.38,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以是最近才这样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:29.64,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,为什么突然就？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:33.27,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:34.56,Default,Darkizumiite 5,0,0,0,,没事！没事！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:35.46,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,好可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:41.88,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,别杀我！别杀我！别杀我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:43.31,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}是小苏！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.14,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,超开心！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:45.68,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,能签名吗？签个名吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:47.18,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,你不杀我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:49.05,Default,Group,0,0,0,,不杀不杀！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:52.76,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小苏 里泉民给了你藏身的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:54.70,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:55.96,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,只是个路人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:09:58.02,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,和小苏你一样被追杀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:10:00.40,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,爱丽丝他们真的死了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:03.80,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,比起死 不如说是消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.72,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,像「气体人第一号」那样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.72,0:10:08.64,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,他们被军人将棋埋伏 然后砰地一声消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:09.40,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,砰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.01,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,真的是爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:15.49,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,我想办法逃掉了 但是剩下的三人变成碎片了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:16.31,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,碎片？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:20.12,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,如果碎片还在 就能让爱丽丝他们复活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:22.67,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,所以浑沌把碎片封印起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:23.55,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:24.53,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,墓碑里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:25.44,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:29.19,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs54\fscx90\bord9\fnTimes New Roman\c&H4E3737&\3c&HD1C0BE&\frz352.8\fax0.1\pos(535.499,388.501)}爱丽丝之墓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:29.19,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs47.999\fscx90\bord9\fnTimes New Roman\c&H4E3737&\3c&HD1C0BE&\fax0.15\frz351\pos(1053,469.501)}拷问铁之墓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:29.19,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs42.001\fscx80\bord9\fnTimes New Roman\c&H4E3737&\3c&HD1C0BE&\fax0.15\frz351\pos(1522.501,537.001)}罂粟粟之墓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:29.65,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,墓碑得用掘墓人专用的镰刀才能打开对吧
Comment: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:34.19,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnTimes New Roman\bord9\c&H98B3D8&\3c&H98B3D8&\pos(880.499,171)}Signature Gutton Candy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.19,0:10:34.19,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnTimes New Roman\bord2.999\c&H92186B&\3c&HA578B8&\pos(880.499,171)} {\c&H4DDCE8&\3c&H494272&}肠花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:31.62,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我看到掘墓人在摆摊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:32.82,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 对的对的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.18,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,收集碎片 然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:35.62,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:36.44,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:39.17,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,把碎片放在传说中的持驹之泉内
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:40.64,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,爱丽丝他们就能复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:41.72,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:44.67,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,那不是之前让件复活的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:47.25,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,书里说 还是很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:49.71,Default,Darkizumiite 5,0,0,0,,无论危不危险 都只有这条路可走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:52.98,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以 我们用武力把掘墓人的镰刀抢过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:54.50,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,用武力把墓碑打开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:57.77,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,用武力把碎片放到持驹之泉里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:10:59.51,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,爱丽丝复活好耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:01.61,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,持驹之泉在哪来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:03.43,Default,Darkizumiite 3,0,0,0,,在浑沌的度假别墅里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:04.63,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这怎么做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:06.08,Default,Darkizumiite 1,0,0,0,,没问题的 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:08.49,Default,Darkizumiite 5,0,0,0,,我们用命从他的度假别墅里偷过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:11.00,Default,Darkizumiite 5,0,0,0,,我们用稀释的碘酊作为替代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:13.58,Default,Darkizumiite 5,0,0,0,,现在进去的话爽不死他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:15.13,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,虽然我不懂但是懂了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:16.45,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,燃起来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.77,0:11:20.56,Default,Guard Walker 1,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:22.38,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「是谁」也太失礼了野！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:25.08,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,步兵N501Y及其四位同伴野！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:25.76,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:26.65,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,东吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:27.71,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,西吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.71,0:11:29.02,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,武藏吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:30.35,Default,Guard Walker 1,0,0,0,,这真是失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:30.99,Default,Guard Walker 2,0,0,0,,所以怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:32.40,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,没有异常野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:34.14,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,美丽的混沌高丽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:35.00,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,佛子佛子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:35.74,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,入间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:36.66,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小手指
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:37.96,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,巢鸭监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.06,0:11:40.41,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,巢鸭监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:41.87,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,监监监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:43.12,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,大叔 这个怎么卖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:44.36,Default,Stall Walker 3,0,0,0,,你笨蛋吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:46.26,Default,Stall Walker 3,0,0,0,,为了庆祝胜利 当然免费
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:47.76,Default,Stall Walker 3,0,0,0,,蝙蝠甲虫都知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:49.55,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那给我们做五个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:51.16,Default,Stall Walker 3,0,0,0,,好好 要五个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:53.05,Default,Stall Walker 3,0,0,0,,压榨内脏三十年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:54.94,Default,Stall Walker 3,0,0,0,,美味到死您且看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.37,Default,Stall Walker 3,0,0,0,,死吧！死！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:58.39,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好厉害！大叔牛哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.39,0:11:59.32,Default,Stall Walker 3,0,0,0,,对吧对吧对吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:00.80,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,做得再大点！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:01.95,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,哟！下一任浑沌！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.32,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,富士见台
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:04.49,Default,Group,0,0,0,,富士见台！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:06.36,Default,Stall Walker 3,0,0,0,,好！我也要鼓足劲干活喽！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:08.24,Default,Stall Walker 3,0,0,0,,搅碎这些糊糊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:13.26,Default,Stall Walker 3,0,0,0,,为啥坏掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:17.83,Default,Stall Walker 3,0,0,0,,像我这样专注于肠花糖领域五十年的匠人\N也会犯这种错误吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:18.63,Default,Stall Walker 3,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:28.40,Default,Group,0,0,0,,所泽泽！所泽泽！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.80,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我感觉不太好诶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:41.15,Default,Group,0,0,0,,{\an8}所泽泽！所泽泽！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.66,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,就用想要杀了她们一样的气势上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:33.99,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一二！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:39.20,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:40.15,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:41.16,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,跟我想象中的不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:45.88,Default,Group,0,0,0,,所泽泽！所泽泽！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:50.84,Default,Group,0,0,0,,{\an8}所泽泽！所泽泽！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.15,0:12:47.74,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好了 该撤了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:51.79,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,好耶！还挺顺利的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:52.85,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,这都多亏了大家的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:53.95,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:12:59.00,Default,Stall Walker 3,0,0,0,,果然是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:00.60,Default,Stall Walker 3,0,0,0,,自杀女在这！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:02.09,Default,Guilt Incarnate,0,0,0,,对不起！觉悟吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:05.38,Default,Stall Walker 3,0,0,0,,{\pos(1099.999,1050.001)}啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:06.21,Default,Guilt Incarnate,0,0,0,,{\pos(1603.999,1050.001)}抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.63,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,小苏 快！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.11,0:13:10.45,Default,Darkizumiite 1,0,0,0,,噢！爱丽丝！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:11.56,Default,Darkizumiite 2,0,0,0,,拷问铁！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.13,Default,Darkizumiite 3,0,0,0,,罂粟粟…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:13.46,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真亏你们能认得出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:14.47,Default,Darkizumiite 2,0,0,0,,光靠气味就足以分辨了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:21.52,Default,Guilt Incarnate,0,0,0,,抱歉 请问你们在做什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:23.44,Default,Guilt Incarnate,0,0,0,,唉 我本来不想这样干的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:32.81,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:33.44,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:34.34,Default,Su-chan,0,0,0,,死了！死了！死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:35.30,Default,Darkizumiite 4,0,0,0,,为什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:36.82,Default,Darkizumiite 4,0,0,0,,难道我们偷错东西了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:37.85,Default,Darkizumiite 5,0,0,0,,绝对不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:40.36,Default,Darkizumiite 2,0,0,0,,难道是持驹之泉的设定被改写了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:41.63,Default,Darkizumiite 5,0,0,0,,那又会是谁干的？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:43.01,Default,Darkizumiite 2,0,0,0,,我也不知道啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:51.92,Default,Guilt Incarnate,0,0,0,,我很抱歉！我很抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:52.99,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:53.40,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:55.09,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实 你这只会起到反效果！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:04.34,Default,Darkizumiite 1,0,0,0,,小苏！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:06.95,Default,Darkizumiite 2,0,0,0,,我们的希望之星 小苏 也消失了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:08.55,Default,Darkizumiite 3,0,0,0,,全完了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:15.04,Default,Group,0,0,0,,O！H！V！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:18.75,Default,Darkizumiite 2,0,0,0,,{\pos(1356,1050.001)}完了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.34,Default,Darkizumiite 3,0,0,0,,{\pos(456,1050.001)}没用了 已经结束了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:20.75,Default,Darkizumiite 5,0,0,0,,{\pos(1392,1050.001)}我们一定会被他们赶尽杀绝！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:22.05,Default,Darkizumiite 1,0,0,0,,{\pos(444,1050.001)}End！Fin！Finito！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:22.77,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}现在放弃还为时尚早！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:24.68,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}对呀 只要努力就一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:25.61,Default,Darkizumiite 4,0,0,0,,{\pos(1348.001,1050.001)}别说这些无关痛痒的废话了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:26.57,Default,Darkizumiite 5,0,0,0,,{\pos(388.001,1050.001)}一切都结束了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:27.83,Default,Darkizumiite 1,0,0,0,,爱丽丝！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:28.81,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}才没这回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:35.35,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你们差不多也该适可而止了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:39.13,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,爱丽丝她们已经不会回来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:41.78,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,曾经发生过的事情永远无法改变！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:44.21,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,事到如今还想后悔也为时已晚了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:45.23,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,都结束了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:49.20,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就算在事后无数次回想当初该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:51.64,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,也已经没有意义了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:02.13,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,所以 只考虑当下力所能及的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:06.98,Default,Darkizumiite 2,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:08.23,Default,Darkizumiite 3,0,0,0,,就像是爱丽丝一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:09.55,Default,Darkizumiite 5,0,0,0,,跟爱丽丝如出一辙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.23,0:15:13.51,Default,Darkizumiite 1,0,0,0,,如果是这孩子的话\N说不定能带我们回到原先那样快乐的世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:14.03,Default,Darkizumiite 5,0,0,0,,去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:14.88,Default,Darkizumiite 4,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.22,Default,Darkizumiite 4,0,0,0,,哟！锵！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:18.01,Default,Darkizumiite 4,0,0,0,,这是爱丽丝遗留下的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.01,0:15:18.71,Default,Darkizumiite 4,0,0,0,,请！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:19.86,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就算你说「请」…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:21.07,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？不会吧？是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:21.72,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我想穿！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:24.43,Default,Darkizumiite 1,0,0,0,,您一定就是我们里大泉的救世主！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:25.96,Default,Darkizumiite 2,0,0,0,,我们一直都在等待着您的到来呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:26.53,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我才不是呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:27.64,Default,Darkizumiite 2,0,0,0,,{\pos(460.001,1050.001)}请换上它吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:28.87,Default,Darkizumiite 3,0,0,0,,{\pos(1488,1050.001)}我来遮住他们的眼睛！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:28.71,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:30.70,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\pos(672,1050.001)}我知道了！让我自己来穿！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:30.42,Default,Darkizumiite 5,0,0,0,,{\pos(1555.999,1050.001)}快！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:35.67,Default,Darkizumiite 2,0,0,0,,根本一模一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:36.22,Default,Darkizumiite 1,0,0,0,,一模一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:38.31,Default,Darkizumiite 4,0,0,0,,除了有些丰满之外简直完美！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:38.99,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,丰满？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:40.39,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:42.62,Default,Group,0,0,0,,P！C！R！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:43.93,Default,Darkizumiite 2,0,0,0,,仔细一看…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.93,0:15:44.60,Default,Darkizumiite 5,0,0,0,,你们也很像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:46.44,Default,Darkizumiite 2,0,0,0,,眯着眼看起来 就跟真货别无二致
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:47.09,Default,Darkizumiite 1,0,0,0,,一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:49.36,Default,Darkizumiite 1,0,0,0,,罂粟粟和拷问铁！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:50.12,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哪里像了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:51.89,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,呃 你们能这么说我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:52.63,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你们太狡猾了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:53.84,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那我呢那我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:54.94,Default,Darkizumiite 1,0,0,0,,那你就 小苏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:55.54,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那就？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:56.30,Default,Group,0,0,0,,拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:15:57.78,Default,Darkizumiite 3,0,0,0,,太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:15:58.30,Default,Darkizumiite 5,0,0,0,,完美！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:16:00.11,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这不就只是 cosplay 吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:01.56,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,能力也没出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.68,Default,Darkizumiite 1,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:05.61,Default,Darkizumiite 1,0,0,0,,我们过去也以为自己只是普通的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:09.38,Default,Darkizumiite 1,0,0,0,,但现在也患上了依赖症\N身心都完全变成了里泉民
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:12.21,Default,Darkizumiite 2,0,0,0,,所以只要你们穿着那身衣服\N说不定也会获得某种力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:14.69,Default,Guilt Incarnate,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 请你们觉悟吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:18.76,Default,Guilt Incarnate,0,0,0,,对不起 请问这是什么？对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:20.60,Default,Walker,0,0,0,,这是红生姜汁吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:21.20,Default,Guilt Incarnate,0,0,0,,眼睛好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:22.83,Default,Darkizumiite 3,0,0,0,,趁现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:28.62,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这是哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:37.25,Default,Group,0,0,0,,{\an8}王手！王手！王手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:34.72,Default,Jonidan,0,0,0,,抓住她们！好好教训一番！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:38.54,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,对了 抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:40.31,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你裙子上挂着的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:41.24,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那个可以变成一张弓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:41.95,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:42.71,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:45.77,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,那是铁线虫先生用雨伞制成的自适应武器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.28,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是我没有箭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:48.77,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,周围卒塔婆有很多嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:50.58,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,诶？ 不会遭报应吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:54.36,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,拜7G事件所赐 应该不存在什么报应了 大概
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:56.24,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:58.37,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不知道你姓甚名谁 总之抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:04.38,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不愧是吾野弓术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:07.92,Default,Guilt Incarnate,0,0,0,,注意 借过借过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:09.23,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,啊嘞？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:16.74,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,刚才是香车 现在是桂马？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:17.80,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这不是军人将棋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:19.84,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,在干什么啊你这个窝囊废
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:21.21,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,明明是在战场上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:22.98,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,再更加混沌一点啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:37.87,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.28,0:17:44.14,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,解开了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:45.45,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,什么解开了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:47.58,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,他们都在遵照将棋的规则移动！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:49.70,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我又不懂将棋的规则！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:52.50,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我意识到这根本不是混沌之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:53.29,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,静留！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:54.78,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,那只三毛猫是将棋的金将
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:55.29,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:56.95,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,金将不能向斜后方移动！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:57.98,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,原来如此 难怪
