Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:06.74,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,真厉害啊 晶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:09.33,Default,Guilt Incarnate,0,0,0,,抱歉！抱歉！抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.68,0:18:11.18,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}罪恶感的化身是香车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:13.44,Default,Guilt,0,0,0,,抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:18.90,Default,Jonidan,0,0,0,,拉腕！拉腕！拉腕！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:18.20,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}等下 停停 好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:19.71,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,玲实！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:20.98,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,序二段是银将
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:23.50,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,他的弱点是左右横向和正后方
Comment: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:32.13,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(152,1)\fs22.5\fnTimes New Roman\bord4.5\c&H2B212D&\3c&H6F4C49&\pos(724.528,507.375)}HERE LIES\NJONIDAN
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:34.47,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,对付桂马的跳跃就得用吾野偏差弓术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.46,0:18:40.80,Default,Rugger Man,0,0,0,,好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:43.68,Default,Rugger Man,0,0,0,,好球！好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:52.02,Default,Rugger Man,0,0,0,,别在意别在意别在意别在意别在意别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:52.91,Default,Rugger Man,0,0,0,,比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:56.47,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,就是现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:01.82,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fscx90\fad(110,1)\fnTimes New Roman\bord7.499\c&H2B212D&\3c&H6F4C49&\pos(936,484.499)}件之墓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.86,0:19:11.06,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:13.26,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,因为是将棋棋子 所以像多米诺骨牌一样一推就倒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.26,0:19:14.17,Default,Walker,0,0,0,,快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:19.36,Default,Walker,0,0,0,,那种事情不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:20.56,Default,Walker,0,0,0,,这个受不了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.56,0:19:22.09,Default,Walker,0,0,0,,逃命吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.09,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:25.61,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,不要抛下王将自己逃跑 你们这些蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:30.45,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,喂 我明白了啊 浑沌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:33.18,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你虽然满嘴混沌 所作所为却根本不混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:35.40,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,看上去你没法摆脱将棋的规则呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:38.55,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什么嘛 只是条憧憬着混沌的宠物狗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:39.46,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:39.97,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,啰嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:41.07,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,我就是混沌的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:43.48,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,再说 没有步兵的将棋就是输棋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:44.74,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,可以放弃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:49.24,Default,Darkizumiite,0,0,0,,{\an8}宰了他！宰了他！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:47.99,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,常盘MAN！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:49.24,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,追加订阅！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:50.47,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,抓住他！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:58.11,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,真是与练爱不相称的古旧设计啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:19:59.59,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,看你们做的好事！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:02.23,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,我要向池袋的魔女王报告你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:04.80,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,叶香公主是绝对不会原谅你们的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:06.81,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:08.89,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香公主是指的叶香吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:10.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,中富叶香？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:13.67,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,亏得你们知道呢 一群边远地区的庸人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:15.71,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,说什么认识的 我们是她的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:17.50,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我们是为了见她才去池袋的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:18.09,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,哈？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:20.74,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,她怎么可能见你们这些臭人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:22.20,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,她可是魔女王叶香啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:25.38,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,池袋 进而是这个世界的恐怖支配者！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:26.15,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,骗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.15,0:20:27.96,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,把你们都蒸成茶碗蒸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.96,0:20:29.32,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,等着瞧吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:30.93,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,通信！通信！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:34.49,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,他说的魔女王是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:38.32,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不过 可以确认叶香没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:39.12,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.12,0:20:41.42,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,浑沌在吓唬人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:44.71,Default,Group,0,0,0,,谢谢你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:47.53,Default,Darkizumiite 6,0,0,0,,大泉学园终于迎来和平了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:53.22,Default,Darkizumiite 3,0,0,0,,请务必保佑我们直到永远 女王爱丽丝大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.22,0:20:55.03,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,诶？做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:58.24,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我们接下来一定要去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:20:59.96,Default,Darkizumiite 1,0,0,0,,那谁来统治这里？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:01.15,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你们自己来呗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:02.97,Default,Darkizumiite 5,0,0,0,,我们都是依赖症啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:05.02,Default,Darkizumiite 5,0,0,0,,步兵他们卷土重来了怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.02,0:21:05.67,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:06.87,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你们自己解决这些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:07.84,Default,Darkizumiite 5,0,0,0,,太没责任了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:08.61,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:10.31,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,好了快把衣服还给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.31,0:21:11.28,Default,Darkizumiite 2,0,0,0,,啊 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:23.29,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:28.47,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那里变成练爱世界的契机 肯定是7G事件吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:32.27,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,然后不知什么时候浑沌和步兵突然复活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:34.62,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,城镇变成了恶人世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:37.15,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,短暂地和平过 为什么会这样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:40.37,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,某人有目的地篡改了练爱世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:41.52,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:42.52,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:46.45,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,他们暂时地获得了军人将棋的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:49.28,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,持驹之泉的设定也被改变了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:55.04,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,全是让人在意的谜团 但果然最在意的还是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:56.04,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:57.03,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.79,0:22:06.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.73,0:22:09.34,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,魔女王？
